article:
This is a 'list of [[Australia]]n [[composer]]s' of classical
music, contemporary music and/or film soundtracks.

These names are largely drawn from the following:
* Music Australia an online service developed by the National Library
  of Australia (NLA) and the National Film and Sound Archive
  (NFSA);
* Australian Music Centre's (AMC) list of "Represented
  artists"; [http://www.australianmusiccentre.com.au/artists
  Australiansmusiccentre.com.au]
* lists entitled "Australian Composers" and "Australian Repertoire" published by
  Australian Choral Conductors Education and Training (ACCET);
* the "Catalogue of Australian Organ Compositions 1866â2002" published by the
  Organ Historical Trust of Australia (OHTA);
* the "Australian Composers" list; [http://www.australiancomposers.com.au/A-
  Z%20Composers/index.html Australiancomposers.com.au] and
* various other websites and media sources.

Wherever possible, dates of birth and death are shown.

The pseudonyms used by some composers are listed along with a reference back to
their legal name.

Personal websites are listed when possible, and entries are cross-referenced to
one or more sources to provide further information.
